# Google Places API (New) key
# 1. Pick a GCP project (recommended: a fresh one for clean billing)
# 2. Enable "Places API (New)" in that project's API Library
# 3. Create an API key under APIs & Services > Credentials
# 4. (Recommended) Restrict the key to: Places API (New) + your IP address
# Then paste the key below and rename this file to .env
GOOGLE_PLACES_API_KEY=
